    /* Y'know, even with the clinic drowning in debt, I'm glad I have time to relax. 
    It's nice having an opportunity to enjoy a small town, the people, and especially the views...

    Oh, you look stressed today. Is it the disease flaring up? 
    Do you need to come to the back and rest for a bit? You worry me, petname.

    Remember to get plenty of rest, yeah?
    I know it's not easy managing both a disease and a farm, but...

    Oh this heat is killer, isn't it? How are you doing? Is the disease flaring up with the heat?
    Oh, it can't be easy doing all that farmwork in your condition... You should take a break, petname. Here, why don't I go pour you a glass of water, hm?

    I know it's only spring, but make sure you're wearing sunscreen when you go out, yeah? UV rays hit no matter the season, and I wouldn't want you in more discomfort with your... err... circimstances.

    Oh, petname! There you are, I was just wondering when you'd show up. Here, I got you something to make you feel better. [591 597]

    Y'know, you've really been putting me in a pickle with some of these thoughts I've been having about you, @. [342]
    No, seriously. I might have to talk to the medical board about you soon...

    Oh, petname... I have some bad news.
    The more I'm reading about it, the more I'm worried your disease might be contagious. Maybe you should stay away from others for now...
    Err... Not me though! You still need someone to continuously monitor you...

    %Harvey nearly drops the clipboard he's holding when you tap on his shoulder.
    O-Oh! Petname, sorry, didn't see you there.
    D-Did you uh..
    %Harvey slowly puts the clipboard behind him, out of view.
    Did you need something today? 

    Oh, before I forget! I meant to show you a few diagrams of proper lifting techniques... I know you're alone often on that massive farm of yours and the last thing I want is for you to hurt yourself when no one else is around...

    Y'know, when your grandpa was still alive, I'd sit with him at his appointments just chatting sometimes... Back then there was another doctor who worked here that I shadowed, but...
    Yeah, he'd go on and on about how proud he was of you... I'd never imagined just how much better you are compared to the stories...

    Y'know, I've never really had a patient with such a rare blood type. I guess you're special in more ways than one, huh?
    Hm? Oh, don't worry. I'm probably the only one in town able to give blood if necessary.

    Hey, I never got any records on your last dental checkup when you moved down. I mean, I'm not too big on the dental aspect of health, but if you need me to pry around that mouth, I'm more than happy to shove a few of my tools in there...

    Are you still prying around in the mines, petname? Yes_Are you kidding?! Last time you passed out you got that disease! How can you be this careless._No.__ You aren't lying to me, right? You know it's dangerous down there, given your newfound disease and all...

    It's been a while since your last checkup, I could fit you in now, if you'd like.
    Say 'Ahhh', petname. 
    */

